Jewish.Mum.of.the.Year.s01e01.Bar.Mitzvah.[MPup]

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/11/21/5c0b70b529563423dedae22044473ac1.png[/img] 

Competitive Jewish mums fight it out with a series of gruelling tasks to win the crown, including challenges to test their cooking, matchmaking, home-making abilities, event organising and how well they know their kids.

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/11/21/9bdaab1feb573042e0ee3a660a1b9cba.jpg[/img]

Jewish.Mum.of.the.Year.s01e02.Matchmaking.[MPup]

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/11/21/e3c84d3e1532e2ff94e9a8bdd31e976c.png[/img]

The six remaining mums are challenged to find 29-year-old Nicola the perfect partner. They split into pairs to find a chap and make him stand out enough to sweep Nicola off her feet.

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/11/21/6dcc2c9cef2b85b277a3c1b4c8daf822.jpg[/img]

Jewish.Mum.of.the.Year.s01e03.Old.Folks.[MPup]

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/11/21/2fbd5f963edf39790ba023a774bf40b9.png[/img]

For the third task the four remaining mums plan a memorable day out to Southend-on-Sea for 22 outspoken Jewish pensioners.

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/11/21/3b874b98eb095f5e8041c1508f10a9a3.jpg[/img]

Jewish.Mum.of.the.Year.s01e04.Friday.Night.Dinner.[MPup]

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/12/05/b9c7813114f0e5bb9da8e71d12defed3.png[/img]

The competition reaches its climax as the remaining mums take turns hosting a traditional Friday night dinner for a party of 16, including family, judges, the other mums, and celebrities including David Baddiel and Jay Rayner.

Friday night dinner is a time for family to come together, an opportunity for a Jewish mum to shine, and an occasion that is as much about the food as it is about the people.

The mums must devise the menu, cook the food, lay the table and host their meal at a boutique north London kosher hotel.

The mums also try their arms at being agony aunt for the Jewish News and answering questions from listeners on a Jewish radio station.

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/12/05/6e38665e925a216411cdd36030ba075c.jpg[/img]
